sequenceDiagram
    participant M  as AI Model
    participant R  as Tool Router
    participant P  as Exec Policy
    participant U  as User
    participant S  as Sandbox
    participant H  as Tool Handler

    M->>R: tool_call(name, args)
    R->>P: check(command)

    alt Auto-approved by rules
        P-->>R: Allow
        R->>S: wrap in sandbox
        S->>H: execute
        H-->>M: result
    else Requires approval
        P-->>R: RequireApproval
        R->>U: show command + context
        U-->>R: Approve / Deny
        R->>S: wrap in sandbox
        S->>H: execute
        H-->>M: result
    else Denied
        P-->>R: Deny
        R-->>M: error: denied
    end
